As an advocate for gender equality + women and girls empowerment … I am proud to be an Ambassador for @AfricanCCF’s life-changing programs in Africa! 
Rural Tanzania can be a difficult place for girls to grow up and thrive. Today is #GivingTuesday, and TOGETHER we can impact thousands of high school girls who live in the western corridor of the Serengeti. 
ACCF’s work focuses on health – menstruation, providing reusable pads, STI’s, reproductive, FGM, career development, confidence and education for these girls. 
For as little as $10, you can help supply one girl with reusable pads for a full year. 
A gift from you today means a lifetime of tomorrows for her.  Donate ▶️ #LinkInBio
